Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for intervening back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you single right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, my phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts... A hangover?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mr. Waiter is finally back. {no idea why he calls kubota a "easy mark; sucker; sitting duck​"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You got any sake with you, Kubota?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just me, \Ncalling at a bad time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't meeting by chance like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,feels nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm practicing \Nfor an upcoming photo shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure I'm doing it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you give me your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful park at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The location's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The stance is good...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Facial expressions while kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you kiss someone, \Nyou close your eyes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't learn much from practicing alone in front of the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is this... really... {\i1}that{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:54.49,Song,,0,0,0,,It so happen lighting in the blue \NSo then you kiss me and tell {it's Sakamoto Hiroshi 坂本洋 - "One And only lover" and... there aren't lyrics anywhere, so joever... hell, forget lyrics I couldn't even find from which album this track is, it's almost as if it was never released outside this ova; not a single word from this line, not idea if it's even engrish or japanese}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:18:02.98,Song,,0,0,0,,This is simple to see for you and me \NTo feel the love so right your love
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:06.40,Song,,0,0,0,,The why have met is just reason to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:10.22,Song,,0,0,0,,I know there's nobody else
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:14.96,Song,,0,0,0,,Who can feel in my blockin' lonely heart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:18.96,Song,,0,0,0,,A place much better than you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:22.46,Song,,0,0,0,,Another day for another life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:26.33,Song,,0,0,0,,No, it's not the way to be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:34.66,Song,,0,0,0,,Look straight ahead and you will see\NThe fantasy that never ends
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:39.38,Song,,0,0,0,,You are my one and only lover
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.43,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we're meant to be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:47.15,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look and you'll discover
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.53,Song,,0,0,0,,A bad thing you need in me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:58.02,Song,,0,0,0,,I can't want no more\NWill you give me a helping hand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:04.34,Song,,0,0,0,,Reach for my heart\NAnd let me be your man
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not fond of alcohol. {person who prefers sweet things to alcoholic drinks}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of a baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A part time job, huh? \NThat's nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go to college too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:20:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a model actually means a life of struggling. \NTo preserve my looks, I have to diet all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:20:05.98,Song,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time \NWhere have you been, babe?{it's "Don't Ever Hurt Me" by Akira Okazawa / 岡沢章, also the 4th track on Tomohito Aoki's (青木智仁) album "double face" for whatever reason; I could find this https://youtu.be/DPQFZRQBSAw?si=F8an6Vc18DhCIX7p without the dialogue on top so gonna translate from that and pray}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I really love sweets.\NI don't remember when I've last had a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, in that case, I'll make you a diet cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:18.28,Song,,0,0,0,,I've been alone in the night \NLonging to hold you in my arms
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Diet cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dietary sweetener instead of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Use low-calorie whip \Ninstead of whipped cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You know so much!\NCan you really make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:30.24,Song,,0,0,0,,Loving you is all that matters\NI'll never face another breakup
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you knowing where to go and what to see around here is even more surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:39.43,Song,,0,0,0,,You would like to be together\NDon't ever leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Kazuya used to take me on dates here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:49.44,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}...chance to believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:21:00.07,Song,,0,0,0,,Say you'll be my girl \NHelp me through the music, babe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:05.96,Song,,0,0,0,,Lost in the cold twilight rain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:12.25,Song,,0,0,0,,Love brings the seasons of change
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:18.04,Song,,0,0,0,,And most of all you'll never know
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota, you know, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:22.89,Song,,0,0,0,,of my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Isn't it Masana?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:43.55,Song,,0,0,0,,Miss you! {Shoji Kumi 障子久美 - Miss you}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:52.01,Song,,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:08.94,Song,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to put it into words\NI could see the love in your eyes {言葉なんかにしなくても\N愛が見えてなね　あの頃\N今はもう　お互い　気持ちなど\N確かめるすべもない}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:17.10,Song,,0,0,0,,Now there's no way for us to know \Nhow we feel about each other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:23.52,Song,,0,0,0,,Where did love go? {　愛はどこへいったの\N　誰かに勝って　何かに負けて\N　何が今　残るというの\N　Miss You\N　このままじゃ　帰り道さえ失くしてゆく\N　向かい合える勇気を　もう一度　与えて}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:29.99,Song,,0,0,0,,You win against someone, \Nyou lose to something else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:33.78,Song,,0,0,0,,But what remains now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.78,0:22:35.37,Song,,0,0,0,,Miss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:41.71,Song,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'll lose my way home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:50.98,Song,,0,0,0,,Give me the courage to face you once again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just do as I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't really be the same Fujisaki I once met...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? \NYou look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.15,0:24:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should rest a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.67,0:24:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I do that? \NWouldn't it be unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! \NI really... don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.21,0:24:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.12,0:24:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that... \NHappened against my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.80,0:24:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can finally say this now, \NI knew about it ever since the junior high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.64,0:24:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.86,0:24:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, because Kazuya was around...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.12,0:24:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.87,0:24:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! W-Wait a minute, Fujisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.55,0:24:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just realized something...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.42,0:25:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, uh... You see... How do I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.26,0:25:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.35,0:25:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just trying to say you don't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.53,0:25:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.50,0:25:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.19,0:25:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't think of me as a slut for having it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.62,0:25:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even ordinary girls have it these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.17,0:25:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.16,0:25:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put it on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.91,0:25:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! No! I'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.72,0:25:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quick about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.31,0:25:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.60,0:25:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. Don't worry \Njust because it's your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.32,0:25:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, that was even quicker than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.77,0:25:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Virgins are such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.65,0:25:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.73,0:25:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.62,0:26:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.85,0:26:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.92,0:26:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fu-Fujisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.31,0:26:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.00,0:26:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She was really tired, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.12,0:26:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, I almost forced her to do it \Nso that I wouldn't be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.31,0:26:48.75,Song,,0,0,0,,Sunrise{(角松敏生) Toshiki Kadomatsu ‎-Premonition Of Summer}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:54.99,Song,,0,0,0,,Daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.43,0:27:01.55,Song,,0,0,0,,My sweetheart
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.92,0:27:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, Kubota.\NI didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.83,0:27:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you've nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.67,0:27:08.34,Song,,0,0,0,,Shining brightly
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.81,0:27:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.72,0:27:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.30,0:27:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I called room service afterwards \Nand ordered smoked salmon, egg sandwich,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.54,0:27:16.26,Song,,0,0,0,,So when your hair's shining brightly
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.41,0:27:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and then also a chicken basket! \NWith a stomach that full, I was fast asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.26,0:27:21.35,Song,,0,0,0,,Oh my love, you belong to me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.35,0:27:24.91,Song,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.11,0:27:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So chill and nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.55,0:27:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you remember the arcades we had near school during our junior high days.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.36,0:27:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know they now have a pizza house there? \NAnd what's more...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.12,0:27:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In the apartment complex to the left of it, \Nroom 203 is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.09,0:27:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a photo shoot tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.13,0:27:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so, could you... \NCould you come the night after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.94,0:27:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can pick up from where we stopped last night, if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.04,0:28:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.72,0:28:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I work night shift the day after tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.44,0:28:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.18,0:28:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. It {\i1}has{\i0} to be the day after tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.63,0:28:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.85,0:28:29.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,200)\bord1\blur1\c&H232429&\3c&HA99FA5&\pos(405.63,221.01)\frz11.6}Kubota stayed out all night!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.85,0:28:29.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,200)\fs15\bord1\blur1\b0\c&H232429&\3c&HA99FA5&\pos(559.96,379.77)\frz15.13}Same clothes as yesterday {あの久保田くんが朝帰り!!!\Nつかれて眠そーな顔\Nきのうと同じ服だ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.85,0:28:29.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,200)\fs15\bord1\b0\blur1\c&H232429&\3c&HA99FA5&\pos(544.79,320.38)\frz13.87}Tired and sleepy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.18,0:28:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazushi, what are you doing in the kitchen \Nbefore you even had a lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.62,0:28:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be feeling my butt to say that, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.05,0:28:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that strange cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.32,0:28:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Strange" sounds a bit rude, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.52,0:28:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? "Healthy cake?" \NI think I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.93,0:29:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.56,0:29:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.03,0:29:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That "healthy cake" is just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.08,0:29:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Will they feel good eating it? \NWon't they get fat?"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.69,0:29:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are always concerned for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.00,0:29:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you think that you should put your own personal needs forward more forcefully sometimes? {unsure what he means: でも時には自分を多少強引なぐらいさらけ出すことが必要な時ってあるんじゃないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.77,0:29:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get slapped for being too pushy, \NI'll be here to comfort you! {"forcefully" in previous line}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.71,0:29:59.99,Song,,0,0,0,,Through an opening between the passing umbrellas {行き交う傘のすきまから\N見えた横顔\N花散る春にまたたいた\N時を隔てて}{Shoji Kumi 障子久美 - 「うすべにの嵐」}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.61,0:30:04.11,Song,,0,0,0,,I saw a profile
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.55,0:30:11.71,Song,,0,0,0,,In the spring of scattering petals
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.42,0:30:17.19,Song,,0,0,0,,Separated by time
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.03,0:30:23.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Love cried and cried, {愛は泣きながら\N思い出を許し やがて\Nせつないまごころになる\Nあさい夢のように}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.00,0:30:29.72,Song,,0,0,0,,Forgiving you in memories {yes, forgiving not forgetting, literally what the song says}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.72,0:30:41.82,Song,,0,0,0,,It becomes a painful sincerity, \Nlike a pale dream
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.82,0:30:53.75,Song,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll see off my chance that is long gone {ああ 遠去かる偶然を見送るから\Nああ 何もかも流して\Nうすべにの嵐}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.75,0:31:04.96,Song,,0,0,0,,Ah, the pink storm washes everything away
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.58,0:31:39.36,Song,,0,0,0,,As I follow the trail \Nof the falling flowers with my eyes {ひたすら降る花の行方\N目で追ううちに}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.61,0:31:53.04,Song,,0,0,0,,The trampled asphalt \Nmarks where the fading starts {ふみにじられたアスファルト\Nうつろいの果て}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.04,0:32:03.17,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,3000)}When did love manage to outlive the hatred... {愛はいつからか\Nにくしみを越えて やがて}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.34,0:32:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.62,0:32:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.22,0:32:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.81,0:32:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to show you, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.97,0:32:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.68,0:32:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.17,0:32:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The graduation album from our junior high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.34,0:33:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nostalgic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:33:00.82,0:33:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After I saw you the other day, I suddenly felt like looking at it, and searched for it like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.93,0:33:06.93,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\b0\frz16.56\bord1\blur1\pos(474.86,351.69)\c&H4D3E42&\3c&HC3C6C8&}Nishi Junior High School, Class 3-B {西中学校\N3年B組}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.93,0:33:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.43,0:33:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And here are you, \Nsitting in front row, so small and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.43,0:33:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us have changed so much \Nin these four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.61,0:33:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.44,0:33:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I grew up by about 20 centimeters \Nwhile I was in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.32,0:33:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't recognize you right away when I saw you in Roppongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.77,0:33:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and to be frank, \Nthat was hella painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.42,0:33:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.45,0:33:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, do you remember \Nwhat I said two nights ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.24,0:33:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That I knew about your feelings \Never since junior high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.96,0:33:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you came to my rescue at the disco, \NI thought you might still have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.50,0:33:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.82,0:33:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,must be a cruel woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.43,0:34:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.23,0:34:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.53,0:34:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you say that \Nit absolutely had to be tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.61,0:34:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, this seems strangely rushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.51,0:34:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.27,0:34:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now is too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.62,0:34:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell you that I love you. {lit: earlier, much earlier than now, I fell in love with you}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.09,0:34:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry! \NCould you wait a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.67,0:34:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.61,0:34:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.76,0:34:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here,\Nat this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.90,0:34:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, am I imposing? \NI didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.91,0:35:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me with those eyes.\NI just came to pick up some things I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.40,0:35:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Things you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.87,0:35:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.12,0:35:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kubota.\NCan you sit over there and wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.21,0:35:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki, did you live together?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.65,0:35:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.80,0:35:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it is a riposte to me or whatever, \Nat least I'm not the only bad guy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.33,0:35:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Us living together was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.80,0:35:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were\Nsuch a possessive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.90,0:35:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You over there, I'm gonna\Ngive you a good piece of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.61,0:35:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Masana may have a pretty face,\Nbut she has her own unhealthy sides too. {lit: she's quite into this - no idea what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.33,0:35:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.60,0:36:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go. You and I have nothing to fight over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.31,0:36:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.56,0:36:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.08,0:36:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.44,0:36:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubota, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.79,0:36:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Kawahara, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.65,0:36:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, he's a horrible guy. \NAll the things those girls said at the disco were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.26,0:36:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.67,0:36:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, he's just an awfully shy person. {tereya?}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.60,0:36:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, he's an incredibly pure person. \NI would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.10,0:36:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... \NThat's why I was dating him for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.77,0:37:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.42,0:37:13.13,Song,,0,0,0,,You'll realize that everything {移りゆくものは全て　幻とわかるだろう\N歌い続けることの意味　気付く時はいつも\N君へのこの想いがある\Nそれは変わることのできないもの}{Toshiki Kadomatsu 角松敏生 - DESIRE}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.37,0:37:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I guess I can only be with someone who will only look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.38,0:37:20.68,Song,,0,0,0,,that moves on is just an illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.38,0:37:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki, please say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.37,0:37:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't this will really be the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.92,0:37:34.75,Song,,0,0,0,,Whenever I realize what it means \Nto keep singing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.22,0:37:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.75,0:37:42.46,Song,,0,0,0,,I have this feeling for you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.29,0:37:50.15,Song,,0,0,0,,It's the one thing that can't change
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.08,0:38:01.79,Song,,0,0,0,,Oh desire, time is not just for forgetting, {Oh DESIRE　時は忘れゆくためにだけ\Nあるものじゃないさ　MY LOVE DESIRE\N何ものにも　しばられないで　この愛を続けてゆく\Nそれが未来へとむかう真実}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.79,0:38:11.03,Song,,0,0,0,,It's not there for you or for me, \Nso my love desire
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.03,0:38:22.18,Song,,0,0,0,,Let's not let anything weigh us down, \Nkeep this love alive
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.18,0:38:35.44,Song,,0,0,0,,That is the truth leading us into the future
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.83,0:38:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.84,0:39:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazushi, don't get too hung up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.11,0:39:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, you'll find \Na better girl than Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.51,0:39:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This cake isn't very sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.26,0:39:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazushi, did you know Yagi is still a virgin \Ndespite always talking so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.55,0:39:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.73,0:39:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.37,0:39:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's dangerous!
